## Local Build (for contributors / reviewers)

If you have cloned the repository and want to build the image yourself:

```bash
# Build from source
docker build -t {{ project_name }} .

# Run with local data
docker run --rm \
  -v "$PWD/data":/workspace/data:ro \
  -v "$PWD/plots":/workspace/plots \
  {{ project_name }}

# Interactive shell for debugging
docker compose run shell
```

