## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| `permission denied` on `plots/` | `chmod 777 plots/` then re-run |
| Container exits immediately | Run `docker compose run shell` and inspect logs |
| `uv.lock` mismatch error | Rebuild the image: `docker compose build --no-cache` |
| Plots are empty / wrong | Check that `data/` matches the expected layout in `README.md` |

